// BuildFeedbackEmail generates an HTML-formatted email for user feedback
// Parameters:
//   - fromAddr: sender's email address
//   - toAddr: recipient's email address (support team)
//   - userName: name of the user submitting feedback
//   - subject: subject of the feedback
//   - feedbackContent: detailed feedback content
